dash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n其他文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eQRAf8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeQRAf8V.jpg&h=94035568&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxszwHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxszwHf.jpg&h=447d79f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vn5dNfC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvn5dNfC.jpg&h=d7993458&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bNZmV8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbNZmV8X.jpg&h=954a77a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60umV8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60umV8Y.jpg&h=4df00706&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NAhutZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NAhutZ.jpg&h=fd7af745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n最後我想做返少少呼籲，今個禮拜唔需要勇武。唔係話活動性質唔適合，亦唔係因為要勇武休息。而係因為每當勇武出場，警察同就會有大量濫權、蓄意傷害他人等嘅柒事發生，前兩禮拜發生太多呢啲事，以致<span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣嘅「製作、散播、發酵」完全唔夠時間做</span>，坊間&mdash;&mdash;尤其一班中老人，完全消化唔切呢埋爆炸性數量嘅資訊。<br />\n<br />\n勇武們，請留返少少時間俾文宣組處理你哋打返嚟嘅成果。"},{"pid":"f5a7150df7fc92bdc7af52e8b9b7575fd6407f1e","tid":1472764,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:07:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ce1ae8888ba5c801bad6700a5bc07dddcfe158","tid":1472764,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:07:56.000Z","msg":"816 816<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr